          "对不稳定草图直接拉伸，导致后续布尔复杂度升高。"
        ],
        "recommendedBefore": [
          "sketch.rectangle",
          "sketch.circle",
          "sketch.polygon",
          "sketch.fromCurve"
        ],
        "recommendedAfter": [
          "transform.translate",
          "boolean.subtract",
          "display.color"
        ],
        "stabilityNotes": [
          "构造类 action 通常是从草图阶段进入实体阶段的关键分界点。"
        ],
        "inputExpectation": "输入通常来自这些类型之一：geom3。",
        "outputMeaning": "输出是二维草图/截面，没有厚度，通常需要进一步构造为实体。",
        "example": {
          "id": "construct_project_example",
          "action": "construct.project",
          "params": {
            "source": "body",
            "axis": "z",
            "mode": "orthographic"
          }
        }
      }
    },
